## Practice Areas

- Estate Planning: Wills, revocable living trusts, irrevocable trusts, durable powers of attorney, living wills, healthcare directives. [https://www.ament.law/practice-areas/estate-planning/]
- Probate & Trust Administration: Petition for grant of letters, Short Certificates, inheritance tax returns (REV-1500), estate accountings, Orphans' Court filings. [https://www.ament.law/practice-areas/probate-administration/]
- Real Estate Settlement Services: Title insurance (Chicago Title, First American), residential and commercial closings, title searches, buyer representation. [https://www.ament.law/practice-areas/real-estate-law/]
- For Sale By Owner (FSBO): Legal services for PA homeowners selling without a realtor — agreement of sale, seller disclosures, title search, deed prep, closing. Flat fees. [https://www.ament.law/practice-areas/for-sale-by-owner/]
- Business Formation & Services: LLC, corporation, partnership formation; operating agreements; contract drafting; commercial leases; compliance. [https://www.ament.law/practice-areas/business-formation/]
- Elder Law: Medicaid planning, long-term care planning, asset protection, guardianship. [https://www.ament.law/practice-areas/elder-law/]

